    Classes in org.eclipse.jetty.server.handler that implement EagerContentHandler.ContentLoaderFactory
    Modifier and Type
    Class
    Description
    static class 
    EagerContentHandler.FormContentLoaderFactory
    An EagerContentHandler.ContentLoaderFactory for MimeTypes.Type.FORM_ENCODED content, that uses FormFields.onFields(Request, Charset, int, int, Promise.Invocable) to asynchronously load and parse the content.
    static class 
    EagerContentHandler.MultiPartContentLoaderFactory
    An EagerContentHandler.ContentLoaderFactory for MimeTypes.Type.MULTIPART_FORM_DATA content, that uses MultiPartFormData.onParts(Content.Source, Attributes, String, MultiPartConfig, Promise.Invocable) to asynchronously load and parse the content.
    static class 
    EagerContentHandler.RetainedContentLoaderFactory
    An EagerContentHandler.ContentLoaderFactory for any content, that uses Retainable.retain() to eagerly load content with zero copies, until all content is read or a maximum size is exceeded.
